<h1 class="h1s">Actors</h1>
<div class="sharethis-inline-share-buttons st-center st-has-labels  st-inline-share-buttons st-animated" style="height:60px;" id="st-1"><div class="st-total ">

<div class="combi_pagedesc" id="intro"> <p>Actors are professional performers who portray a given character in a dramatic production on stage or in motion pictures. Even though the term actor is basically used to refer to a male performer, it is becoming increasingly common to use it as a gender neutral term. Theater as an artistic means of expression and entertainment began evolving in ancient Greece and the known history of acting dates back to around 534 BC when Thespis, of Icaria, became the first person ever to portray a character in a play on stage. Acting as a profession has come a long way over the centuries, and so have actors. Initially acting was not considered a respectable profession, and few, if any, educated and well-to-do people chose to pursue acting as a career. But now times have changed and acting is an honorable profession just like any other and there are colleges and institutions dedicated to the grooming of aspiring performers into skilled actors. There are different types of actors, some like experimenting with versatile roles while others prefer specializing in a certain genre of acting like comedy, horror, or romance. You will find information about the life and works of various actors from all over the world in this section.</p> </div>

The formidable actor later went on to work in movies like <em>The Illusionist</em>, <em>The Incredible Hulk</em>, <em>The Birdman</em> and <em>American History X</em>. Norton ventured into film direction with <em>Keeping the Faith</em>. He also supports various environmental and social causes.</p></div></div></article></div><div class="clear"></div><div class="wrapper"><article class="feature col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 eventstart internal_space"><h2 class="ptitle"><span class="number">&nbsp;53&nbsp;</span><a class="tileLink" href="//www.thefamouspeople.com/profiles/jeff-bridges-30212.php">Jeff Bridges</a></h2><div class="image col-lg-4 col-md-5 col-sm-5 col-xs-12"><a class="tileLink" href="//www.thefamouspeople.com/profiles/jeff-bridges-30212.php"><img class="img-responsive combi-profile-img" src="//www.thefamouspeople.com/profiles/thumbs/jeff-bridges-1.jpg" alt="Jeff Bridges" title="Jeff Bridges"></a><div style="text-align:center;"><i onclick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'CatVote', 'Up-Vote-Clicked', 'Jeff Bridges']);" class="fa fa-thumbs-o-up like-btn-30212" data-id="30212" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="Vote for Your Favourite "></i><i onclick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'CatVote', 'Down-Vote-Clicked', 'Jeff Bridges']);" class="fa fa-thumbs-o-down dislike-btn-30212" data-id="30212" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="Vote for Your Favourite "></i><div class="clear"></div><span class="likes likes-30212">27</span><span class="dislikes dislikes-30212">6</span></div></div><div class="col-lg-8 col-md-7 col-sm-7 col-xs-12 rt-text-display"><div class="desc-q"><b>Famous As: </b>Actor</div><div class="desc-q"><b>Birthdate: </b>December 4, 1949</div><div class="desc-q"><b>Sun Sign: </b>Sagittarius</div><div class="desc-q"><b>Birthplace: </b>Los Angeles, California, United States</div><div class="desc descEvent"><p>Considered one of the most celebrated actors of his generation, Jeff Bridges is known for his natural acting and his versatility. A vintage car and sports car collector, Dempsey has competed in events, such as the <em>Rolex 24 at Daytona</em>, <em>24 Hours of Le Mans</em>, and <em>Baja 1000</em>. Dempsey is also known for his&nbsp;philanthropic workS.</p></div></div></article></div><div class="clear"></div><div class="wrapper"><article class="feature col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 eventstart internal_space"><h2 class="ptitle"><span class="number">&nbsp;290&nbsp;</span><a class="tileLink" href="//www.thefamouspeople.com/profiles/joseph-frank-keaton-945.php">Buster Keaton</a></h2><div class="image col-lg-4 col-md-5 col-sm-5 col-xs-12"><a class="tileLink" href="//www.thefamouspeople.com/profiles/joseph-frank-keaton-945.php"><img class="img-responsive combi-profile-img" src="//www.thefamouspeople.com/profiles/thumbs/buster-keaton-3.jpg" alt="Buster Keaton" title="Buster Keaton"></a><div style="text-align:center;"><i onclick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'CatVote', 'Up-Vote-Clicked', 'Buster Keaton']);" class="fa fa-thumbs-o-up like-btn-945" data-id="945" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="Vote for Your Favourite "></i><i onclick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'CatVote', 'Down-Vote-Clicked', 'Buster Keaton']);" class="fa fa-thumbs-o-down dislike-btn-945" data-id="945" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="Vote for Your Favourite "></i><div class="clear"></div><span class="likes likes-945">23</span><span class="dislikes dislikes-945">5</span></div></div><div class="col-lg-8 col-md-7 col-sm-7 col-xs-12 rt-text-display"><div class="desc-q"><b>Famous As: </b>Actor, Director</div><div class="desc-q"><b>Birthdate: </b>October 4, 1895</div><div class="desc-q"><b>Sun Sign: </b>Libra</div><div class="desc-q"><b>Birthplace: </b>Piqua, Kansas, United States</div><div class="desc-q"><b>Died: </b>February 1, 1966</div><div class="desc descEvent"><p>Buster Keaton was an American comedian, filmmaker, actor, and stunt performer. Regarded as one of the greatest actor-directors of all time, Keaton was renowned for his physical comedy. Counted among the greatest stars of classic Hollywood cinema by the <em>American Film Institute</em>, Buster Keaton's films remain highly regarded. His 1926 film <em>The General </em>was admired by actors like Orson Welles.</p></div></div></article></div><div class="clear"></div><div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12 col-sm-12" style="margin:10px 0px;"><div class="center-ad desktop_ad">

However, his dark comedy has often been called insensitive and offensive by several critics.</p></div></div></article></div><div class="clear"></div><div class="wrapper"><article class="feature col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 eventstart internal_space"><h2 class="ptitle"><span class="number">&nbsp;312&nbsp;</span><a class="tileLink" href="//www.thefamouspeople.com/profiles/john-paul-cusack-1892.php">John Cusack</a></h2><div class="image col-lg-4 col-md-5 col-sm-5 col-xs-12"><a class="tileLink" href="//www.thefamouspeople.com/profiles/john-paul-cusack-1892.php"><img class="img-responsive combi-profile-img" src="//www.thefamouspeople.com/profiles/thumbs/john-cusack-3.jpg" alt="John Cusack" title="John Cusack"></a><div style="text-align:center;"><i onclick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'CatVote', 'Up-Vote-Clicked', 'John Cusack']);" class="fa fa-thumbs-o-up like-btn-1892" data-id="1892" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="Vote for Your Favourite "></i><i onclick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'CatVote', 'Down-Vote-Clicked', 'John Cusack']);" class="fa fa-thumbs-o-down dislike-btn-1892" data-id="1892" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="Vote for Your Favourite "></i><div class="clear"></div><span class="likes likes-1892">27</span><span class="dislikes dislikes-1892">5</span></div></div><div class="col-lg-8 col-md-7 col-sm-7 col-xs-12 rt-text-display"><div class="desc-q"><b>Famous As: </b>Actor</div><div class="desc-q"><b>Birthdate: </b>June 28, 1966</div><div class="desc-q"><b>Sun Sign: </b>Cancer</div><div class="desc-q"><b>Birthplace: </b>Evanston, Illinois, United States</div><div class="desc descEvent"><p>John Cusack started his career as a teen actor. In 2018, he donated $100,000 to the <em>National Alliance on Mental Illness</em>.</p></div></div></article></div><div class="clear"></div><div class="wrapper"><article class="feature col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 eventstart internal_space"><h2 class="ptitle"><span class="number">&nbsp;354&nbsp;</span><a class="tileLink" href="//www.thefamouspeople.com/profiles/adrien-brody-4447.php">Adrien Brody</a></h2><div class="image col-lg-4 col-md-5 col-sm-5 col-xs-12"><a class="tileLink" href="//www.thefamouspeople.com/profiles/adrien-brody-4447.php"><img class="img-responsive combi-profile-img" src="//www.thefamouspeople.com/profiles/thumbs/adrien-brody-2.jpg" alt="Adrien Brody" title="Adrien Brody"></a><div style="text-align:center;"><i onclick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'CatVote', 'Up-Vote-Clicked', 'Adrien Brody']);" class="fa fa-thumbs-o-up like-btn-4447" data-id="4447" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="Vote for Your Favourite "></i><i onclick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'CatVote', 'Down-Vote-Clicked', 'Adrien Brody']);" class="fa fa-thumbs-o-down dislike-btn-4447" data-id="4447" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="Vote for Your Favourite "></i><div class="clear"></div><span class="likes likes-4447">23</span><span class="dislikes dislikes-4447">5</span></div></div><div class="col-lg-8 col-md-7 col-sm-7 col-xs-12 rt-text-display"><div class="desc-q"><b>Famous As: </b>Actor, Producer</div><div class="desc-q"><b>Birthdate: </b>April 14, 1973</div><div class="desc-q"><b>Sun Sign: </b>Aries</div><div class="desc-q"><b>Birthplace: </b>Woodhaven, New York, United States</div><div class="desc descEvent"><p>Adrien Brody is best known for his <strong>Academy Award</strong>-winning performance as Polish pianist Władysław Szpilman in <strong>The Pianist</strong>. Renowned for his contribution across all three major acting mediums, Molina has received nominations for prestigious awards, such as <em>Tony Awards </em>and <em>Screen Actors Guild Awards</em>. Apart from acting, Alfred Molina works toward spreading awareness about AIDS. He has also been donating towards AIDS research.</p></div></div></article></div><div class="clear"></div><div class="wrapper"><article class="feature col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 eventstart internal_space"><h2 class="ptitle"><span class="number">&nbsp;898&nbsp;</span><a class="tileLink" href="//www.thefamouspeople.com/profiles/tony-curtis-6205.php">Tony Curtis</a></h2><div class="image col-lg-4 col-md-5 col-sm-5 col-xs-12"><a class="tileLink" href="//www.thefamouspeople.com/profiles/tony-curtis-6205.php"><img class="img-responsive combi-profile-img" src="//www.thefamouspeople.com/profiles/thumbs/tony-curtis-6205-1.jpg" alt="Tony Curtis" title="Tony Curtis"></a><div style="text-align:center;"><i onclick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'CatVote', 'Up-Vote-Clicked', 'Tony Curtis']);" class="fa fa-thumbs-o-up like-btn-6205" data-id="6205" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="Vote for Your Favourite "></i><i onclick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'CatVote', 'Down-Vote-Clicked', 'Tony Curtis']);" class="fa fa-thumbs-o-down dislike-btn-6205" data-id="6205" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="Vote for Your Favourite "></i><div class="clear"></div><span class="likes likes-6205">24</span><span class="dislikes dislikes-6205">6</span></div></div><div class="col-lg-8 col-md-7 col-sm-7 col-xs-12 rt-text-display"><div class="desc-q"><b>Famous As: </b>Actor</div><div class="desc-q"><b>Birthdate: </b>June 3, 1925</div><div class="desc-q"><b>Sun Sign: </b>Gemini</div><div class="desc-q"><b>Birthplace: </b>New York, United States</div><div class="desc-q"><b>Died: </b>September 29, 2010</div><div class="desc descEvent"><p>Tony Curtis was an American actor who achieved the height of his fame in the 1950s and 1960s in a career spanning six decades. Also a well-known philanthropist, Tony Curtis helped fund the rebuilding of the <em>Great Synagogue</em> in Hungary. In 1998, he founded a non-profit organization called <em>Emanuel Foundation for Hungarian Culture</em>, which works towards the restoration of synagogues.</p></div></div></article></div><div class="clear"></div><div class="wrapper"><article class="feature col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 eventstart internal_space"><h2 class="ptitle"><span class="number">&nbsp;899&nbsp;</span><a class="tileLink" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mark_Consuelos" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Mark Consuelos</a></h2><div class="image col-lg-4 col-md-5 col-sm-5 col-xs-12"><img class="img-responsive combi-profile-img" src="//www.thefamouspeople.com/profiles/thumbs/mark-consuelos-1.jpg" alt="Mark Consuelos" title="Mark Consuelos"><div style="text-align:center;"><i onclick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'CatVote', 'Up-Vote-Clicked', 'Mark Consuelos']);" class="fa fa-thumbs-o-up like-btn-46537" data-id="46537" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="Vote for Your Favourite "></i><i onclick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'CatVote', 'Down-Vote-Clicked', 'Mark Consuelos']);" class="fa fa-thumbs-o-down dislike-btn-46537" data-id="46537" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="Vote for Your Favourite "></i><div class="clear"></div><span class="likes likes-46537">18</span><span class="dislikes dislikes-46537">4</span></div></div><div class="col-lg-8 col-md-7 col-sm-7 col-xs-12 rt-text-display"><div class="desc-q"><b>Famous As: </b>Actor</div><div class="desc-q"><b>Birthdate: </b>March 30, 1971</div><div class="desc-q"><b>Sun Sign: </b>Aries</div><div class="desc-q"><b>Birthplace: </b>Zaragoza, Aragón, Spain</div><div class="desc descEvent"><p>Best known as <em>Mateo Santos</em> from<em> All My Children</em> and as <em>Hiram Lodge</em> from <em>Riverdale</em>, Mark Consuelos was born to an Italian mother and a Mexican father in Spain. He was also a talented photographer and was associated with several boards.</div></div></article></div><div class="clear"></div><div class="wrapper"><article class="feature col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 eventstart internal_space"><h2 class="ptitle"><span class="number">&nbsp;1148&nbsp;</span><a class="tileLink" href="//www.thefamouspeople.com/profiles/dudley-moore-3759.php">Dudley Moore</a></h2><div class="image col-lg-4 col-md-5 col-sm-5 col-xs-12"><a class="tileLink" href="//www.thefamouspeople.com/profiles/dudley-moore-3759.php"><img class="img-responsive combi-profile-img" src="//www.thefamouspeople.com/profiles/thumbs/dudley-moore-3.jpg" alt="Dudley Moore" title="Dudley Moore"></a><div style="text-align:center;"><i onclick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'CatVote', 'Up-Vote-Clicked', 'Dudley Moore']);" class="fa fa-thumbs-o-up like-btn-3759" data-id="3759" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="Vote for Your Favourite "></i><i onclick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'CatVote', 'Down-Vote-Clicked', 'Dudley Moore']);" class="fa fa-thumbs-o-down dislike-btn-3759" data-id="3759" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="Vote for Your Favourite "></i><div class="clear"></div><span class="likes likes-3759">18</span><span class="dislikes dislikes-3759">4</span></div></div><div class="col-lg-8 col-md-7 col-sm-7 col-xs-12 rt-text-display"><div class="desc-q"><b>Birthdate: </b>April 19, 1935</div><div class="desc-q"><b>Sun Sign: </b>Aries</div><div class="desc-q"><b>Birthplace: </b>Charing Cross, London, England</div><div class="desc-q"><b>Died: </b>March 27, 2002</div><div class="desc descEvent">Dudley Moore was a prominent figure of the 1960s’ British satire boom. descEvent"><p>James Mason was an English actor known for his work in both British cinema and Hollywood. One of the most bankable actors during the mid-1940s, Mason became the first person to be honored with the <em>BAFTA Award </em>for<em> Outstanding British Film</em>. He is credited with saving Buster Keaton's reels of nitrate film, which he discovered in Keaton’s previously owned house.</p></div></div></article></div><div class="clear"></div><div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12 col-sm-12" style="margin:10px 0px;"><div class="center-ad desktop_ad">

Widely regarded as one of the greatest comedy performers of all time, Rik Mayall received several posthumous honors after sudden and untimely death at the age of 56.</p></div></div></article></div><div class="clear"></div><div class="wrapper"><article class="feature col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 eventstart internal_space"><h2 class="ptitle"><span class="number">&nbsp;1344&nbsp;</span><a class="tileLink" href="//www.thefamouspeople.com/profiles/richard-jenkins-44558.php">Richard Jenkins</a></h2><div class="image col-lg-4 col-md-5 col-sm-5 col-xs-12"><a class="tileLink" href="//www.thefamouspeople.com/profiles/richard-jenkins-44558.php"><img class="img-responsive combi-profile-img" src="//www.thefamouspeople.com/profiles/thumbs/richard-jenkins-1.jpg" alt="Richard Jenkins" title="Richard Jenkins"></a><div style="text-align:center;"><i onclick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'CatVote', 'Up-Vote-Clicked', 'Richard Jenkins']);" class="fa fa-thumbs-o-up like-btn-44558" data-id="44558" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="Vote for Your Favourite "></i><i onclick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'CatVote', 'Down-Vote-Clicked', 'Richard Jenkins']);" class="fa fa-thumbs-o-down dislike-btn-44558" data-id="44558" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="Vote for Your Favourite "></i><div class="clear"></div><span class="likes likes-44558">17</span><span class="dislikes dislikes-44558">3</span></div></div><div class="col-lg-8 col-md-7 col-sm-7 col-xs-12 rt-text-display"><div class="desc-q"><b>Famous As: </b>Actor</div><div class="desc-q"><b>Birthdate: </b>May 4, 1947</div><div class="desc-q"><b>Sun Sign: </b>Taurus</div><div class="desc-q"><b>Birthplace: </b>DeKalb, Illinois</div><div class="desc descEvent">Richard Jenkins is best known for his <strong>Academy Award</strong>-nominated roles in <strong>The Shape of Water </strong>and <strong>The Visitor</strong>. <script type="text/javascript">
(function($) {
	$('#showmore').css({"cursor":"pointer","color":"green","background-repeat":"no-repeat","background-position":"252px 3px","font-size": "14px"});
    $('.award_section').hide();
    $('#showmore').click(function () {
        $(this).toggleClass("open").toggleClass("close");
        $(this).next().toggle();
	$(this).css("display", "none");

    });
	$.fn.scrollPagination = function(options) {
		var pcondition = '["102","2"]';
		var c1 = 	'category_parent';
		var c2 =  "";
		var c3 =	"1";
		var limit = 10;
		var settings = {
			nop     : 10,  		// The number of posts per scroll to be loaded
			offset  : limit,  // Initial offset, begins at 0 in this case
			error   : 'No More Profiles!', // When the user reaches the end this is the message that is
			               		// displayed. You can change this if you want.
			delay   : 0, 			// When you scroll down the posts will load after a delayed amount of time.
			                	// This is mainly for usability concerns. You can alter this as you see fit
			scroll  : true, 	// The main bit, if set to false posts will not load as the user scrolls.
			                	// but will still load if the user clicks.
			sqlcondition: pcondition,
			c1:c1,
			c2:c2,
			c3:c3
		}

		// Extend the options so they work with the plugin
		if(options) {
			$.extend(settings, options);
		}

		// For each so that we keep chainability.
		return this.each(function() {

			// Some variables
			$this = $(this);
			$settings = settings;
			var offset = $settings.offset;
			var busy = false; // Checks if the scroll action is happening
			                  // so we don't run it multiple times

			// Custom messages based on settings
			if($settings.scroll == true) $initmessage = 'Scroll for more or click here';
			else $initmessage = 'View More';

			// Append custom messages and extra UI
			$this.append('<div class="content"><\/div><div class="loading-bar">'+$initmessage+'<\/div>');

			function getData() {
				// Post data to ajax.php
				var url    = '//www.thefamouspeople.com/ajax/page_loader.php';

				$.post(url, {
				    action    : 'scrollpagination',
				    number    : $settings.nop,
				    offset    : offset,
					sqlc  : $settings.sqlcondition,
					c1    : $settings.c1,
					c2    : $settings.c2,
					c3    : $settings.c3,

				}, function(data) {
					var data = data.trim();
					// Change loading bar content (it may have been altered)
					$this.find('.loading-bar').html($initmessage);
					// If there is no data returned, there are no more posts to be shown. Show error
					if(data.length == 0) {
						$this.find('.loading-bar').hide();
						//$this.find('.loading-bar').html($settings.error);
					}
					else {
						// Offset increases
					    offset = offset+$settings.nop;
						// Append the data to the content div
					   	$this.find('.content').append(data);
						//$('img').loadScroll(1);
						// No longer busy!
						busy = false;
					}
				});
			}
			function getDataContent() {
				// Post data to ajax.php
				var url    = '//www.thefamouspeople.com/ajax/page_loader.php';

				$.post(url, {

					action  : 'scrollpagination',
				        number  : $settings.nop,
				        offset  : offset,
					sqlc	: $settings.sqlcondition,
					c1	: $settings.c1,
					c2	: $settings.c2,
					c3	: $settings.c3

				}, function(data) {

					var data = data.trim();

					// Change loading bar content (it may have been altered)
					$this.find('.loading-bar').html($initmessage);

					// If there is no data returned, there are no more posts to be shown. Show error
					if(data.length == 0) {
						$this.find('.loading-bar').hide();
						//$this.find('.loading-bar').html($settings.error);

					}
				});
			}

			getDataContent(); // Run function initially

			// If scrolling is enabled
			if($settings.scroll == true) {
				// .. and the user is scrolling
				$(window).scroll(function() {
					// Check the user is at the bottom of the element
					if($(window).scrollTop() + $(window).height() > $this.height() && !busy) {
						// Now we are working, so busy is true
						busy = true;
						// Tell the user we're loading posts
						$this.find('.loading-bar').html('Loading Posts');
						// Run the function to fetch the data inside a delay
						// This is useful if you have content in a footer you
						// want the user to see.
						setTimeout(function() {
							getData();
						}, $settings.delay);
					}
				});
			}

			// Also content can be loaded by clicking the loading bar/
			$this.find('.loading-bar').click(function() {
				if(busy == false) {
					busy = true;
					getData();
				}
			});
		});
	}

	$.fn.loadScroll = function(duration) {
	var $window = $(window),
	images = this,
	inview,
	loaded;

	images.one('loadScroll', function() {
		if (this.getAttribute('data-src')) {
			this.setAttribute('src',
			this.getAttribute('data-src'));
			this.removeAttribute('data-src');
			if (duration) {

				$(this).hide()
					   .fadeIn(duration)
					   .add('img')
					   .removeAttr('style');
			} else return false;
		}
	});

	$window.scroll(function() {
	inview = images.filter(function() {
		var a = $window.scrollTop(),
			b = $window.height(),
			c = $(this).offset().top,
			d = $(this).height();
		return c + d >= a && c <= a + b;
	});

	loaded = inview.trigger('loadScroll');
	images = images.not(loaded);
    });
	};

})(jQuery);

	       profileName: e })
	      .done(function (e) {});
	}*/
</script>

function openwin(nm, width, height) {
    var name = nm;
    if (pop && !pop.closed) {
        pop.close();
    }
    pop = eval("window.open('" + name + "','NewWIN','chrome[4],toolbar=no,left=5,top=5,width=" + width + ",height=" + height + ",directories=no,menubar=no,SCROLLBARS=yes,left=2,right=2')");

}

    window.close();
